# JsonPages Platform

Next.js 16 App Router SaaS backend. React 19, Tailwind 4, Supabase Auth + DB, Vercel hosting.

## Directory structure

- `src/app/api/v1/` — public API (33 route handlers)
- `src/app/api/internal/` — admin/cron endpoints (internal token auth)
- `src/app/dashboard/` — authenticated dashboard (projects, domains, leads, billing)
- `src/lib/` — shared server-side libraries
- `docs/api/README.md` — API endpoint inventory and detailed docs
- `docs/flows/` — per-endpoint flow documentation (one .md per endpoint group)
- `supabase/` — DB schema and migrations
- `scripts/` — test and utility scripts

## Auth model

- **Provider:** Supabase Auth with GitHub OAuth
- **API auth:** `requireRequestUser(req)` validates session, returns user + githubLogin
- **Tenant access:** `assertTenantAccess({ userId, tenantId, requiredRole })` checks role via `tenants.owner_id` or `tenant_members`
- **Roles:** `owner | admin | editor` (hierarchical)
- **Webhook auth:** HMAC signatures (LemonSqueezy: `x-signature`, Resend: Svix headers)
- **Tenant API auth:** `Authorization: Bearer <tenant_api_key>` for content/save routes
- **Internal auth:** `requireDomainsAdmin` or `x-cron-secret` / `x-preview-refresh-token` (valore atteso in env `TENANT_PREVIEW_INTERNAL_TOKEN` per le route tenant-preview)

## Key libraries

- `src/lib/tenantContentStore.ts` — tenant content CRUD (Supabase, replaces Edge Config for hot path)
- `src/lib/serverAuth.ts` — auth helpers
- `src/lib/saveFeatureFlags.ts` — `SAVE2ROUTES_BETA`, `SAVE_HOT_ENABLED`, `SAVE_REPO_ENABLED`
- `src/lib/customDomains.ts` — domain validation, governance, rate limiting
- `src/lib/vercelDomains.ts` — Vercel Domains API wrapper
- `src/lib/licensing.ts` — billing intent state machine
- `src/lib/tenantPreview.ts` — screenshot preview tenant (Playwright + Blob), allowlist host, bypass protezione Vercel opzionale

## External integrations

- **Supabase:** auth, tenants, billing_intents, leads, domains, tenant_content
- **GitHub App:** repo creation, file commits, installation management
- **Vercel:** project creation, deployments, domains, Edge Config (save2repo only)
- **LemonSqueezy:** checkout, subscriptions, customer portal
- **Resend:** email delivery for form submissions
